B-uUby5uNSWsZrnibdvQrVFTT8RAhfep27dQZd7XAJzg&oe=67694326"}, {"file_name": "screenshotMenu.png", "id": "9210961488948872", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39036606_9210961495615538_4622789879229780214_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=JMOV9M54Kj0Q7kNvgFn16C0&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAcJ4ggsBqgdvxdDM4y5-ItZfIPG3NcZWbmPp0tUv0LdQ&oe=6769342D"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "2560X1440.png", "id": "842965181141388", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974759_842965184474721_1485266597461374600_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=otLyhv1JIeMQ7kNvgFf2Jbv&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDVwpDA7phoRxEp7kgSiD4YgK6JpP9z2szGdNU0bvcoTg&oe=67693894"}, "display_name": "Lacrosse", "keywords": ["lacrosse", "lax"], "long_description": "**Lacrosse Skills: Immersive Lacrosse in Virtual Reality**\n\nDive deep into the thrilling world of lacrosse like never before with LAXVR Skills, an unparalleled virtual reality experience. Crafted for both enthusiasts and novices, this game offers a chance to immerse yourself fully in the realm of lacrosse from a first-person perspective. Here's a glimpse into what awaits you:\n\n1. **Four Main Game Modes:** \n   **Shooting Mode:** Hone your shooting skills, master different techniques, and aim for that perfect shot.\n   **Goalie Mode:** Stand tall between the posts, anticipate your opponent's moves, and make that crucial save.\n   **Defender Mode:** Learn the art of defense, stop the attackers in their tracks, and reclaim the ball.\n   **The Medicine Game:** Embark on a historical journey that pays homage to the deep-rooted origins and traditions of lacrosse. Experience the soul of the game and its spiritual significance.\n\n2. **Casual Play Modes:** \n   **Wall Ball:** Perfect for those who cherish the simple joys of the game. Bounce, catch, and repeat. Sharpen your hand-eye coordination and reflexes.\n   **Free Shoot:** Sometimes, all you need is the open field, a stick, a goal, and a ball. Practice your shots or just enjoy the serenity of the virtual field.\n\n3. **Community and Competition:** \n   **Leaderboards:** Push your limits! Challenge yourself, compete with your friends, and see how you rank globally in the LAX VR community. ", "short_description": "Pick up a stick and elevate your lacrosse game! Engage in thrilling drills: fire precision shots, stuff attackers, and de-twig attackers with decisive checks. Can you score a 2-pointer past our goalie? Stop a 12-yard step down shot? Or shut down an attacker's split dodge? Challenge awaits in every corner!"}]}, "developer_name": "Duper Studios", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://laxvr.com/privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Duper Studios", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.laxvr.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_SOME", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2776542286000603"}, {"id": "331529188132278"}, {"id": "459781504968480"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "27689844393996384"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974860_441126119038352_2884899896599361267_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=PaljVGCCX9sQ7kNvgEz59NR&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC10wSO9lIGNar